'''MinasTirith.com''' was founded on [[May 21]], [[2000]] by White Gold Wielder ("WGW"), and was active up until early [[2021]] when it went offline for unknown reasons, making it one of the longest running [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]] online communities. The forum was known for their scholarly discussions and tight-knit community.
